collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT a.id as user_id, a.user_name, a.password, a.nama_lengkap, a.level_id, b.keterangan AS level_ket, a.unit_id, c.nm_unit, a.is_active, a.is_login FROM `user` `a` INNER JOIN `user_level` `b` ON `a`.`level_id` = `b`.`id` LEFT JOIN `unit` `c` ON `a`.`unit_id` = `c`.`id` WHERE `a`.`user_name` = 'admin'
